{"word":"G1307 - διαφανής - diaphanḗs - dee-af-an-ace' - Transparent","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διαφανής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diaphanḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-af-an-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Transparent</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தெளிவுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"transparent, translucent"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and <a href=\"#/G5316 - φαίνω - phaínō - fah'-ee-no/5316\">G5316</a>; <i>appearing through</i>, that is, &ldquo;diaphanous&rdquo;: - transparent.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}